# QA / tooling output — screenshots, reports, harness scratch.
# Scoped BY LOCATION, deliberately NOT by extension: 251 images in this repo are real
# data (the imagery documents the pipeline extracts from under corpus/, and the vendored
# offline map tiles under frontend/public/tiles/). A blanket *.png would break both.
.gstack/
tmp/qa/fixshots/
tmp/qa/**/*.png
**/screenshots/